ReadCase
data.value: select top(1) T1.NUMB from CKT_LEGAL_ACT_PERS T5 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_CASE T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_LA_PER_LA_CROL T4 with(readuncommitted) on T1.NUMB = T4.CAS_NUM on (T5.LA_PERSON_ID = T4.LAP_ID) and (T5.ACCOUNT_TYPE = 'R') and (@ladRNumber = T5.LAD_R_NUMBER) and (@lgaRIdentifier = T5.LGA_R_IDENTIFIER)

data.name: ReadCaseAssignment
data.value: select top(1) REASON_CODE, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, SPD_ID, OFF_ID, OSP_CODE, OSP_DATE, CAS_NO from CKT_ASSIGN_CASE where (REASON_CODE = 'RSP') and (@casNo = CAS_NO) order by EFFECTIVE_DATE desc

data.name: ReadCollectionObligationTypeCsePerson
data.value: select T1.COLL_ID, T1.APPLIED_TO_CD, T1.COLL_DT, T1.ADJ_IND, T1.CONCURRENT_IND, T1.CRT_TYPE, T1.CST_ID, T1.CRV_ID, T1.CRD_ID, T1.OBG_ID, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.OTR_ID, T1.OTR_TYPE, T1.OTY_ID, T1.COLL_ADJ_DT, T1.CREATED_TMST, T1.OB_TRN_AMT, T1.CT_ORD_APPLIED_TO, T2.DEBT_TYP_ID, T2.DEBT_TYP_CD, T2.DEBT_TYP_CLASS from CKT_OB_TYPE T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_COLLECTION T1 with(readuncommitted) on (T2.DEBT_TYP_ID = T1.OTY_ID) and (T2.DEBT_TYP_CLASS <> 'R') and (T1.CONCURRENT_IND = 'N') and ( ( (T1.CREATED_TMST > @createdTmst1) and (T1.CREATED_TMST < @createdTmst2) and ( ( (T1.ADJ_IND = 'Y') and (T1.COLL_ADJ_DT > @collAdjDt) ) or (T1.ADJ_IND = 'N') ) ) or ( (T1.CREATED_TMST < @createdTmst1) and (T1.ADJ_IND = 'Y') and (T1.COLL_ADJ_DT between cast(@date as date) and cast(@collAdjDt as date)) ) ) and (T1.CREATED_TMST < @createdTmst2) and (T1.CRT_TYPE <> 2) and (T1.CRT_TYPE <> 7) and (T1.COLL_ID > @collId) order by T1.COLL_ID

data.name: ReadCollectionType
data.value: select top(1) T1.COLLECTION_TYPE_ID from CKT_COLLTN_TYPE T1 join CKT_CR_DETAIL T2 on (T1.COLLECTION_TYPE_ID = T2.CLT_IDENTIFIER) and (T2.CRD_ID = @crdId) and (T2.CRV_IDENTIFIER = @crvIdentifier) and (T2.CST_IDENTIFIER = @cstIdentifier) and (T2.CRT_IDENTIFIER = @crtIdentifier)

data.name: ReadCseOrganization
data.value: select ORGANZTN_ID, TYPE_CODE from CKT_CSE_ORGANIZATN with(readuncommitted) where TYPE_CODE = 'J' order by ORGANZTN_ID

data.name: ReadCsePerson
data.value: select top(1) T1.NUMB from CKT_CSE_PERSON T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OB_TRN T3 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.NUMB = T3.CSP_SUP_NUMBER) and (T3.CPA_SUP_TYPE is not null) and (T3.OTY_TYPE = @otyType) and (T3.OB_TRN_TYP = @obTrnTyp) and (T3.OB_TRN_ID = @obTrnId) and (T3.CPA_TYPE = @cpaType) and (T3.CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (T3.OBG_GENERATED_ID = @obgGeneratedId)
